From dea98f47565efe9bc7cbdb7778d9744cf2cb3018 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Tue, 23 Jun 2026 10:59:27 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(checkout): add tax, discount code form, and complete
 order/payment flow
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Add 10% VAT (مالیات بر ارزش افزوده) to basket totals (view + server)
- Add discount code form with live validation endpoint (/payment/discount)
- Checkout now posts gateway, addressId and discountCode
- Rewrite createPayment to compute totals server-side, apply discount,
  attach shipping address/details, and persist the order
- Wire payment router (was unmounted) and add verifyPayment + payment-result view

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 <noreply@anthropic.com>
Claude-Session: https://claude.ai/code/session_019fhmuc7ZofnhXQGM2EDkKu
